Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:12.74,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:27.42,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:27.42,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:33.59,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:33.59,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.10,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.10,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:44.60,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:44.60,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.15,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:56.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:56.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:01.74,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:01.74,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.42,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.42,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.21,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.21,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:34.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hagu-chan, you haven't met him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:39.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:43.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai used to live in our apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:51.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He had strong arms... and a friendly smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was really an amazing senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.26,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\c&H93A9E7&\bord0.1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs50\be1\3c&HB3C5E6&\frz333.584\pos(177,464)}Dreamy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.57,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\bord0.1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs120\fscy80\be1\3c&HB3C5E6&\move(1159,393,-410,393)\c&H84A0E8&}Dreamy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:11.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys get so dreamy when we talk about Lohmeyer-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's an amazing person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:25.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I met Lohmeyer-senpai for the\Nfirst time, some time after I met Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of somen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.64,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\c&H0F2E40&\bord0\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs50\b0\pos(148,163)}Meat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:41.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Meat! I want to eat meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:44.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me meat, meat, meat, meat, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:46.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, making a fuss won't get us any meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:49.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Payday hasn't arrived yet, so it's hard going...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No more somen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's complaining about my family's somen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.78,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz331.72\bord0\shad0\fnChickenscratch\fs40\move(537,556,745,205)\c&H283B48&}MEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat it if you don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me meat! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why Morita-san would go off like that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't eaten meat in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes things rough, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As young adults, living without meat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:20.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had the smell of meat for aroma\Ntherapy, maybe it'd calm us down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:21.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs30\bord1.5\be1\shad0\c&H3B5972&\3c&HADD8E6&\pos(233,319)}Japanese Beef
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:21.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs30\bord1.5\be1\shad0\c&H3B5972&\3c&HADD8E6&\pos(630,326)}Meat Juice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.72,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,950)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord0.1\be1\fs30\fsp5\fscy70\shad0\3c&H4FA4C6&\c&H346961&\pos(435,115)\t(0,1500,\fs120}Waft
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:27.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't satisfy our hunger, so it'd just make things twice as hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. Mayama-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:38.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning to ask you... this room has been empty for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't anyone moving in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that room is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That room is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That room is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That room is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lohmeyer-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,German? Foreign student?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our senpai, and he's on leave from school at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,His father fell ill, so he's helping out on his family's farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:20.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Mayama-senpai look so sad before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a person was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:31.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was serene like the northern plains...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful, lustrous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:41.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fragrant, firm, yet juicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.35,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Juicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,600)\bord0\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fs50\fsp2\frx12\fry348\frz348.507\move(610,300,725,50)\c&H96BD9C&}Poetic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:44.35,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArchitext\bord0.01\b0\fs35\be1\shad0\frx0\fry328\c&H949EA5&\3c&H949EA5&\pos(208,275)}Poet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.64,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Boxes: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Tomato
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:49.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you all been doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.71,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.46,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs60\bord2\be1\shad0\fscx70\fsp3\3c&HE5F2F8&\c&H253744&\pos(539,324)}Japanese?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.75,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he's popular?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.42,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs80\bord0.01\be1\shad0\fscy80\fsp3\c&HBBA4E9&\3c&HA2B1E9&\pos(586,329)}Popular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:18.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually came back yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:23.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bus as I'd missed work for a while, I went\Nto say hi and got caught up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)\bord1\shad0\c&HE5F1F9&\be1\3c&H525FC1&\fs16\fsp-1\frx4\fry8\frz17.779\pos(633,321)}Store\NOwner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)\bord0\shad0\fs13\fscx80\fsp-1\frz359.606\c&H829CA7&\pos(694,183)}Roast Ham
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,0)\bord0\shad0\fs13\fscx80\fsp-1\frz359.606\c&H829CA7&\pos(780,177)}Boneless Ham
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well? We were all worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! Today, we celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs80\bord0.01\be1\shad0\fscy80\fsp3\c&HBBA4E9&\3c&HA2B1E9&\pos(555,331)}Popular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.32,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's popular here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I brought you guys plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:37.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:39.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\3c&HE0E7E8&\c&H5E666D&\move(431,211,431,431)}Boneless Ham
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sausage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat 'til you're full!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:44.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:58.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're almost expired, so we gotta eat them all tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:05.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This flavor and aroma! Just what you expect from an expensive ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Its juicy and full-bodied flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:15.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start delivering ham again, so I'll bring plenty for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:18.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's a tomato we grew back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:27.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes so well with the sausage. It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Oh, and you're a newcomer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:30.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takemoto, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.04,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs60\fscy85\bord0\shad2\4c&H98A4E9&\c&HBCC3F3&\pos(707,46)}Already in love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So you're Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:36.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:43.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Senpai, how is your father doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:51.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time until we harvest the rice, and my older brother\Nand his wife are taking care of the fields and cows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:55.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I gotta make some money over here until harvest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:57.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to graduate already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,His arm and chest are so built...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He really looks like a working man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:07.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he gets stranded on a deserted island,\Nit looks like he could sustain a family of six.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... he's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.20,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnArtificeSSK\fs35\b0\fscx75\bord2\be1\shad0\c&H755495&\3c&HBFA8F4&\frz3.386\pos(154,53)}Once again in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.00,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\fscx80\fs50\frx358\fry16\frz2.027\c&HDBEAF0&\pos(725,108)}Rice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:15.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so it's time to be looking for jobs in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:21.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you can't find a place to work, then come to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of you. I won't let you go hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:38.15,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second there, I almost understood what\Na girl feels when someone proposes to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.53,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And two weeks later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.12,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscx70\bord0.1\be1\shad1\fs45\c&HFAFFFE&\3c&HF8FEFD&\4c&H8C8F8C&\pos(661,369)}And two weeks later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:08:01.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The plentiful food left everyone feeling magnanimous...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And our ability to work got better and better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:06.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The happy and juicy days were endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so we thought....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ham-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Please give us ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:37.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't treat us cruelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a note from Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.34,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Letter: {\be1\3c&H000000&}I have no choice but to go home again. I'm going home for a bit. — Lohmeyer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:51.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,His father's sick again, so he's going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ham-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}Come back—!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:16.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving everyone at the apartment with\Njuicy memories and empty stomachs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:25.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Senpai. Farewell, ham. Farewell, oh, juicy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto, have you finished that thing yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The place to put Hagu-chan's "kokoro"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:39.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Rococo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I pulled an all-nighter two nights ago to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:51.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, finishing that job makes me want to give myself a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:51.95,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Poster says Legendary Hero Search
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.12,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArtificeSSK\bord1\be1\shad0\fscx60\fs50\fsp1\c&H12161B&\3c&H83D0FA&}Legendary{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&} Hero Search
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:55.87,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArtificeSSK\bord1\be1\shad0\fscx60\fs50\fsp1\c&H12161B&\3c&H83D0FA&}Legendary Hero{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&} Search
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArtificeSSK\bord1\be1\shad0\fscx60\fs50\fsp1\c&H12161B&\3c&H83D0FA&}Legendary Hero Search
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.75,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Poster says Legendary Hero Search
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:03.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once again searching for a legendary hero"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:07.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Arakawa Land that rundown park by the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They had a character like that, Mayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:14.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What's wrong, Mayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've turned into a shoujo manga character!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you don't know about it, Takemoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a few years already, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are we on a grassy knoll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:36.41,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Arakawa Land
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fallen into disrepair now, but at one time, he was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A legendary hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mama. Where's the kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko wants a picture with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Michiko! Be careful not to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:53.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dear, is the photo session with the mascot on the flyer really today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:00.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this character has a weird hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:04.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz346.6\frx358\fry356\move(572,48,509,153)\fscy80\bord0.01\fsp3\be1\shad0\c&H383327&\fnArchitext\3c&H383327&}Arakawa Land
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:04.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H1C252D&\fsp-1.5\frz340.628\move(326,158,264,260)\3c&HCBDAE3&\frx4\fry344}Photograph\NSession!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:04.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H1C252D&\fsp-1.5\move(730,67,660,175)\t(0,7616,\fs26)\frx28\fry348\frz346.793}Nyanzaburou
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this thing a dog, a cat, or a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:09.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of theme parks out there these days,\Nso getting people to come must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:12.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably impossible with just one character...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There's the kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too b-b-b-big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.26,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp2\shad0\fscy80\fs50\t(0,1567,\fs70)\pos(437,303)\c&H3A444E&\3c&H17191A&}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:09.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, kitty! Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a picture! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko! Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko, Ryoko, you both have hearts popping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Take a pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the...? That's rude of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking someone else's wife like that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa and the kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with this trashy park?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:57.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You three! Haven't I told you to stop smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:04.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we at a place like this for our school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:05.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\bord1\shad0\be1\3c&HEEF5F2&\c&H596767&\t(0,898,\fs50)\pos(454,162)}Stomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna crack your head open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? You wanna mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:23.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing? Lemme down, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Masa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:25.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Masa-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Don't mess with us! Let Masa down, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H1F2538&\fs40\bord1.5\be1\shad0\move(566,109,610,60)\frz15.086\3c&H4952B0&}Thud
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,His stomach feels like it has a steel plate in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Teru's punch couldn't even budge him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:44.14,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's tall, his arms are strong, and his chest is amazingly thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:49.44,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And most of all, this manliness flowing out\Nof him, even when covered with fur...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.94,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to follow him forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:58.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a big man like you, Nyanzaburou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please take a picture! I'll give you my cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'll never smoke again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:15.17,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Showa 46 = 1971
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:15.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Arakawa Land in the Suginami District was\Nopened in the 46th year of Showa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:21.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}...when the biggest landlord in the Hamadayama area, Mr. Arakawa\NNinzaburou, opened up part of his land as a park to contribute to the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:25.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,0)\move(678,33,626,26)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs35\b0\bord1.5\shad0\c&H4F595F&\3c&HCCE3E8&\t(0,8577,\fs28}Trademark{\c&H7CB8C3&} hairstyle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:25.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,0)\move(728,256,656,199)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs35\b0\bord1.5\shad0\c&H4F595F&\3c&HCCE3E8&\t(0,8577,\fs28)}Loves {\c&H9BABDE&}cats
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:25.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,0)\move(200,273,237,211)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs35\b0\bord1.5\shad0\c&H4F595F&\3c&HCCE3E8&\t(0,8577,\fs28)}The cat{\c&HB094B8&} hates {\c&H4F595F&}him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:25.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,0)\move(28,96,105,79)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs35\b0\bord1.5\shad0\3c&HCCE3E8&\t(0,8577,\fs28)\c&H8C9AE8&}Trading cards{\c&H6C7C83&} of {\c&HD8BBA9&}his favorite\N{\c&H56676B&}Tokusatsu heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:25.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it had a fair amount of visitors when it first opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:35.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}Time passed, and the park was steadily losing customers, facing\Ncompetition from the larger theme parks that opened in other cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:45.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}And in the first year of Heisei, in order to make a comeback and revitalize\Nthe town, Arakawa himself came up with a mascot character.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.65,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Heisei 1 = 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was Nyanzaburou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:47.83,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs45\fscx80\bord1.5\shad0\be1\pos(679,67)\3c&HE3F8FF&\c&H446D89&}Nyanzaburou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:54.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The park director, Arakawa Ninzaburou's love for Tokusatsu,\Ncats, hero characters, and his own tacky hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:59.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...were put together in a weird mixture to create this dicey character.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:05.01,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord0.5\shad0\fscy80\be1\c&HA99992&\move(344,415,344,60)}Nyanzaburou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:05.01,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord0.5\shad0\fscy80\be1\move(340,475,340,118)\c&H7289E1&}Memorial
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:05.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was no way they could've\Nmade a comeback with such a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H6F7F85&\fscx65\fsp2\fs50\pos(501,360)}Route
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Arakawa was troubled by the ever-falling number of visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"How can we shine the light of hope onto our Arakawa Land?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know so much, Mayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:21.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, they actually have a memorial like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a savior suddenly appeared in front of Arakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was truly a messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:40.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,During the two years that person worked as Nyanzaburou,\Nthe number of visitors was ten times greater than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.76,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(100,387,18,387)\b0\fs30\be1\bord1\shad0\fscx70\3c&HECE6E3&\c&H867D78&}200/day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.76,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(618,32,540,32)\b0\fs30\be1\bord1\shad0\fscx70\3c&HECE6E3&\c&H6D605A&}2000/day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:48.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, how could just changing the person inside the\Nmascot increase the number of visitors by that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it happened, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.65,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\be1\shad0\fs14\c&HABBAB6&\3c&HF2FCFD&\pos(270,130)}Daily Visitors\N200
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.65,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\be1\shad0\fs14\c&HABBAB6&\3c&HF2FCFD&\pos(607,137)}Daily Visitors\N2000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's way too different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:59.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Left Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}First Generation Suit\N {\be1\3c&H635514&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:59.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Right Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Legendary Nyanzaburou Suit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The arms and legs are too long, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The original Nyanzaburou was 167cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:11.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So only male applicants shorter than 167cm were being accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the person who came to the interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.67,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Interview Room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the poster looking for a person to work as a mascot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:29.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a huge man who was over 190cm tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:35.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking through job listings, and I found this poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:35.85,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Poster: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Part-time job as a Mascot character "Nyanzaburou"\NGive dreams to the Children!!!\NCreate the future for the district!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:40.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And since it's just weekends, I was hoping you guys could hire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:46.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I liked the line, "Give dreams to the children!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hired!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.54,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\fscy90\be1\shad0\fsp2\fs60\c&H646DD2&\3c&HE7ECF4&\pos(742,71)\frz333.434\frx354\fry358}Hired
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:58.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Director, the costume is for people shorter than 167cm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just lenghten the arms and legs of the costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:05.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting the future of Arakawa Land on this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when was that at stake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:12.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was the beginning of the legendary\Ndays that lasted for two short years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:17.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.27,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\bord0.01\shad0\fs22\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscx75\be1\3c&HE9F1F4&\c&H6D757C&\pos(581,434)}Arakawa Ninzaburou &
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So you were inside that thing, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:26.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend and the fact that the visitors increased\Nby tenfold all makes sense now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally understand, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:35.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai, with his powerful arms and friendly smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:41.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The senpai that I admire, who I can't see anymore because\Nhe went home to take over his family's farm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The senpai who proudly fed us vegetables that he grew himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:52.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The senpai who told everyone to come to his\Nplace if we couldn't find a place to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:53.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.77,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Surrounding Nyanzaburou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:09.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture is from the party celebrating the 100,000th visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing number...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:09.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H5D71C8&}Congratulations\N{\3c&H000000&}Over 100,000 visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, they're all old people and men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:19.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the majority of the visitors\Nto the park were old people and men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:27.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knew that Nyanzaburou was no hero, but\Njust a costume with Lohmeyer-senpai inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:28.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:36.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We, who had already become adults, can\Nnever hope to be embraced again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:43.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet there are times when we want to be held tightly by arms\Nthat are stronger than ours, just like when we were kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I was a child, just like the way my father and mother used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:54.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a drama of the two years that Lohmeyer-senpai created.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:56.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the mike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is there a gallery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:04.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer! Lohmeyer! Lohmeyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:12.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohmeyer-senpai, who surrounded everyone\Nwith his unwavering kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:18.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We all get lonely and want to go flying to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:23.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But who is there to hold you when you're feeling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:30.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I get discouraged by the smallest\Nthings, I was thinking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still didn't know what I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:40.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I decided for myself that I can't just say, "Things\Nare fine the way they are," and give up on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,550)\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fscx80\fsp3\fs55\c&HE8E8E8&\bord1\be1\pos(444,322)}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:49.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Arakawa Land afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:20:03.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find a one-yen coin on the side of the road
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:07.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pounce on it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:14.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All money are lonely creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave them alone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:22.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you care for them in your yellow wallets
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:39.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll bring along more of their money friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:47.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}They'll bring more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:55.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Rah-rah, please bring more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:58.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're ringing up that wad of bills."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A new hero who can sing and dance appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:14.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And, with his daily concerts, he gripped the hearts of the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:17.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Arakawa Land entered its second golden age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:28.23,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:28.23,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:33.36,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:33.36,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:40.49,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:40.49,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.58,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.58,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:50.33,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:50.33,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:53.42,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.87,0:21:53.42,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.38,0:22:00.80,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:22:00.80,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:06.72,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:06.72,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:12.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:12.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:19.15,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:19.15,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:25.29,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:25.29,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
